TIPS FOR ACCEPTING FAILURE AND MOVING ON

Why is solo traveling popular?

What do you think about the following quote?

To awaken quite alone in a strange town is one of the pleasantest sensations in the world.
Freya Stark

1. Itinerary (n) /aɪˈtɪnərəri/: a detailed ​plan or ​route of a ​trip:
2. Travel agent (n) /ˈtrævl ˈeɪdʒənt/
3. Relaxation (n) /ˌriːlækˈseɪʃn/: the ​feeling of being ​relaxed:
4. Speciality (n) /ˌspeʃiˈæləti/:  ​product that is ​extremely good in a ​particular ​place:
5. Overcome (v) /ˌoʊvərˈkʌm/: ​succeed in ​controlling or ​dealing with something:
6. Unforgettable (adj) /ˌʌnfərˈɡetəbl/


# idioms
Take risks (phrase): to do something even though you know that something bad could happen as a result
It’s all Greek to me (idiom) :something that is impossible to understand.

# structure
Structures with “forget”:
S + forget+ to+ V-infinitive

